id":192824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T07:08:51.000Z","msg":"noted"},{"pid":"3a99ad8e181e7b7361e0a7c43c37a3f8c000be08","tid":1427503,"uid":90882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T07:09:06.000Z","msg":"Noted without thanks"},{"pid":"e377332bc60343f13b6678d7b51ee615547f272b","tid":1427503,"uid":59868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T07:09:17.000Z","msg":"打啦屌你老母，去撚到深圳亮劍<br />\n都唔撚過埋條深圳河落黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f8511bc8d80c85083dcf149a1474515fa98bb1c","tid":1427503,"uid":286057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T07:09:18.000Z","msg":"好驚啊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9703225822ff629c1caab9f4268791dc6d79dc56","tid":1427503,"uid":39838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T07:09:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.whatscap.com/cfe/392/cfe39262ba7ec815f6def14410dde60c4be142ac_b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.whatscap.com%2Fcfe%2F392%2Fcfe39262ba7ec815f6def14410dde60c4be142ac_b.png&h=03f642fd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2e5f8597567c2c2d7b847c14ba86532d4d615d02","tid":1427503,"uid":59773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T07:09:35.000Z","msg":"咁快d出啦"},{"pid":"ff94fde524353ad0d66e0f15bfe69b68e2dc0963","tid":1427503,"uid":296369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"014d67df43d0894990c42ed32ca54b683be01a93","tid":1427503,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:28:36.000Z","msg":"港澳辦及中聯辦就目前香港局勢，在深圳舉行座談會，港區人大代表和政協委員等應邀出席。<br />\n<br />\n基本法委員會前副主任梁愛詩在會後表示，從港澳辦主任張曉明早上的講話中，<span style=\"color: red;\">了解到中央對特區政府及警隊應對現時危機有充分信心，所以未有出手，但不等如中央不會出手，如果遇到動亂，行政長官可以要求解放軍協助，亦可以實施全國性法律。</span><br />\n<br />\n對於有人認為若出動解放軍，即等如「一國兩制」完結，<span style=\"color: red;\">梁愛詩則認為，相關機制並不抵觸「一國兩制」，如果有人破壞「一國兩制」，中央一定會處理。</span><br />\n<br />\n梁愛詩又說，<span style=\"color: red;\">會上曾討論是否成立獨立調查委員會，但目前暴力情況持續，未是成熟進行。</span><br />\n<br />\n一同出席座談會的基本法委員會副主任譚惠珠稱，中央政府堅定支持林鄭月娥行政長官帶領香港依法施政，及堅持支持香港警察依法執法，恢復秩序，並堅定繼續維持「一國兩制」，強調「一國」十分重要，須尊重國旗和國徽，市民要與暴力及暴徒割蓆。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2213801/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2213801%2F&d=BEWB7xVw7%2BU8sFed0V75Z2WYsxP5Z0Wle18NOkmjjC4%3D&h=751352f9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2213801/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T07:09:51.000Z","msg":"本未倒置，係政府唔肯成立獨立調查委員會同回應訴求先引發一連串的激烈抗爭，點可以話抗爭激烈所以未係時候成立，612之後又唔立即成立？？"},{"pid":"b08f9c827076099ff68f69d2d0893869bbfc11b0","tid":1427503,"uid":38651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T07:10:17.000Z","msg":"宵禁 戒嚴 解放軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n快點懲罰我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"582975b7c71425983c4bcb02be7dbf966175474d","tid":1427503,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T07:10:21.000Z","msg":"好悶  快出手啦"},{"pid":"4f9ae47f5b25a27c942ef400a7420296595ca006","tid":1427503,"uid":131782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0b7653bc280a8c537189b145808b620f39988966","tid":1427503,"uid":107927,"like":137,"dislike":0,"score":137,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T06:30:54.000Z","msg":"721無出手咩?<br />\n一個何妖有咁大power叫晒黑白兩道合作?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T07:10:59.000Z","msg":"如果中共無出手 我切柒都唔撚信"},{"pid":"1f99953ea47f76362e40ca778f06745d35b0d1ea","tid":1427503,"uid":238138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T07:11:04.000Z","msg":"快L啲"},{"pid":"dde082f17760a9d540487fb6ce289369e84f7a4e","tid":1427503,"uid":4519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T07:11:35.000Z","msg":"亮劍未呀？"},{"pid":"962129b811bc406d2eca4606988261ee2f9b70e6","tid":1427503,"uid":8257,